data.description: NEW ROOF JUST INSTALLED!!!!! 30-year warranty on the shingles & 5-year warranty on the labor (Meaning if there are any issues within 5 years, the company will come and fix it for free). Seller used the same company that installed the roof 16 years ago and never had ANY issues. $20,000 worth of added value to this home. Come see this beautiful & charming 3 Bed/2 Bath on a HUGE oversized corner lot. .36 Acres. This is a one-owner home. The couple has lived here 36 years and you will see the pride they have taken in homeownership! The home has been meticulously maintained. No HOA & no CDD!! No association to tell you what you can & cannot do. Make the property your own! Lakeland, FL is quickly becoming a destination city. Cherrywood solid wood cabinets in the kitchen (look BRAND NEW), granite countertops, double oven range, stainless steel appliances, brand new garbage disposal, as well as a brand new garage door opener. The home also features a spacious enclosed sunroom that features windows instead of screens(current owner has converted it into an extra room), as well as it being insulated and having central A/C. The sunroom looks out into the beautiful fenced-in backyard featuring an orange tree, deck, & shed. There is so much yard space in the front & back for any activities a big family could dream of! Put in a playground or start a garden! You do not want to miss this chance to call this gorgeous property your home.
